## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of skepticism enhancement. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant information in other languages. Additionally, the lack of specific publication dates for some sources may affect the currency of the information. Further research could explore additional fields and cultural perspectives on skepticism.